### Test User Management API

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7249
@accessToken = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Lấy danh sách users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/User?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Lọc theo role (1=Admin, 2=Teacher, 3=Student, 4=Supervisor)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/User?idVaiTro=3
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Tìm kiếm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/User?searchKeyword=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Lấy chi tiết user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/User/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Tạo user mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/User
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenDangNhap": "teacher02",
  "matKhau": "Teacher@123",
  "email": "teacher02@bantayvang.vn",
  "hoTen": "Phạm Văn C",
  "maNhanVien": "GV002",
  "chucDanh": "Giảng viên",
  "khoaPhong": "Khoa Đào tạo",
  "idVaiTro": 2,
  "trangThai": true
}

### 6. Cập nhật user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/User/2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updated@bantayvang.vn",
  "hoTen": "Tên đã cập nhật",
  "maNhanVien": "GV001",
  "chucDanh": "Giảng viên trưởng",
  "khoaPhong": "CNTT",
  "idVaiTro": 2,
  "trangThai": true
}

### 7. Vô hiệu hóa user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/User/3/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Kích hoạt user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/User/3/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 9. Reset password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/User/3/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPassword": "NewPass@123"
}

### 10. Xóa (deactivate) user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/User/4
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}